Package com.app.service

Interface CrudService<U>

Type Parameters:
U - the type of the entity being managed
All Known Subinterfaces:
ClientService, OrderService, ProductService
All Known Implementing Classes:
ClientServiceImpl, GenericServiceImpl, OrderServiceImpl, ProductServiceImpl
public interface CrudService<U>
A generic interface that provides CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for entities of type CrudService. This interface can be used to implement basic operations for managing entities in a service layer.
